{"id":"140","name":"happy-hour-halfway-there","title":"Happy Hour: Halfway There","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2008-05-21T17:00:00-05:00","tags":["flag","happy hour","memorial day","metro nashville public schools","Nashville","pedrio garci","tennessee","tennessee valley authority","tva"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/2181286369_1aa7043d8c.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-141\" title=\"2181286369_1aa7043d8c\" src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/2181286369_1aa7043d8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\"></a></p><ul><li>The state flag has been flying upside down at Legislative Plaza for at least two days straight. We highly recommend WSMV&#x2019;s video segment about it, because it&#x2019;s really dramatic. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/video/16349431/index.html?rss=nash&amp;psp=news\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>It&#x2019;s been a while since we heard from Pedro (Garcia, former head of Metro Schools), who&#x2019;s how teaching at his <em>alma mater</em> USC. And how did he break the silence? &#x201C;I don&#x2019;t want to talk to anyone right now, especially the <em>Scene</em>.&#x201D; [<a href=\"http://blogs.nashvillescene.com/pitw/2008/05/the_pedro_principle.php\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;blogs.nashvillescene.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Pith In The Wind</a>]</li><li>One wrong click of the mouse and 9 million Tennesseans could be without power. New study shows that the TVA is vulnerable to cyber attacks. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20080521/NEWS/80521124/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>Metro has already planned their sobriety checkpoints for Memorial Day. Be careful out there this weekend. [<a href=\"http://sylvanpark.blogspot.com/2008/05/mnpd-sobriety-checkpoints-planned-for.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;sylvanpark.blogspot.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Sylvan Park</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/crudbud/2181286369/in/pool-nashvillest/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">crudbud</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/05/09/happy-hour-tgif/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Hour: TGIF\">Happy Hour: TGIF</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/04/09/happy-hour-fighting-t